FeedPackage.Description: Framework for Microsoft SharePoint© 2010 and 2013. Allows to map list items to simple hand-writen POCO classes and perform actions by manipulating with entities. - strong typed operations with items - abstract layer on Sharepoint object model - simplifying recurring routine actions - ability to unit test
FeedPackage.Summary: Framework for Microsoft SharePoint© 2010 and 2013. Allows to map list items to simple hand-writen POCO classes and perform actions by manipulating with entities. GOALS: - strong typed operations with items - abstract layer on Sharepoint object model - simplifying recurring routine actions - ability to unit test FEATURES: - create wrappers on a SPSite,SPWeb,SPList - get items by typed query, Id, Guid or specified field - create, update, delete items by typed entity - lazy access to any entity property(Castle Proxy) - typed CAML queries(Caml.NET with extentions) - many other features upcoming
FeedPackage.Tags: Sharepoint Framework ORM POCO UnitTest Wrapper
FeedPackage.Title: SharepointCommon
